      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "QUEEN OF KUNA (4) continues to race well but is struggling to break through, placing at her last four runs. Last start finished 2nd on June 17 over 520m at this track behind Just A Sapphire beaten 3 lengths (30.42) in a Grade 4/5. Has won two of four starts from this draw. Well-placed to take this out. STARLIGHT TORY (3) impressed when clocking a blistering 29.81 over 520m at this track. Top win latest and rates a key player again. TAKE MY ADVICE (6) returned a better run last time, finishing in the money (30.00) at this track behind STARLIGHT TORY in a Grade 5. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Can measure up. CLIFTON LUCA (1) can feature with the right run.",
